org.pitest.mutationtest.engine.gregor

Class AvoidStringSwitchedMethodAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.objectweb.asm.MethodVisitor
      • org.pitest.mutationtest.engine.gregor.AvoidStringSwitchedMethodAdapter

  • public class AvoidStringSwitchedMethodAdapter
extends org.objectweb.asm.MethodVisitor
    Disables mutations in the conditional statements generated by java compilers when switching on a string value. Disable logic looks for a call to hashcode followed immediately by a tableswitch or lookupswitch. Mutation is renabled when the switch block is complete or a new line of code is encountered.
